HC1 robust SE for baseline T5C1. Same coefficient, SE changes from 3.95e-05 to 4.61e-05. Still significant at 5%.
HC3 robust SE for baseline T5C1. Same coefficient, SE changes to 4.68e-05. Still significant at 5%.
Cluster on origin country. Same coefficient, larger SE (5.59e-05). Still significant at 5%.
Cluster on destination country. Same coefficient, largest SE (7.03e-05). Marginally insignificant at 5%.
Cluster on road type. Same coefficient, SE = 5.33e-05. Significant at 5%.
Log-log specification: log(taubar) ~ log(distance) + internatl. Positive elasticity (0.125). Significant at 5%.
Semi-log: log(taubar) ~ distance + internatl. Positive and highly significant (p<0.001).
Quadratic in distance. Linear term positive but insignificant (p=0.59); quadratic term also insignificant.
Asinh(taubar) as outcome. Positive distance coefficient, significant at 1%.
Per-km trade cost as outcome, internatl as treatment. International links have higher per-km costs. Significant at 5%.
Median regression (50th percentile). Positive distance coefficient, highly significant.
25th percentile regression. Positive distance coefficient, significant at 1%.
75th percentile regression. Positive distance coefficient, significant at 1%. Larger magnitude than median.
Distance only (no internatl dummy). Positive, significant at 1%.
International dummy only (no distance). Positive, highly significant.
Add road type dummies to baseline. Distance coefficient stable, significant at 1%.
Distance x road type interactions. Paved road distance coefficient positive but marginally insignificant.
Kitchen sink with road type dummies + population. Distance coefficient stable, significant at 1%.
Separate population dummies (one500, both500) instead of atleastone500. Distance coefficient stable.
Add michpaved indicator. Distance coefficient attenuated but still significant at 5%.
Add all Michelin road type indicators. Distance coefficient attenuated, significant at 5%.
Per-ton-km cost as outcome. Negative distance coefficient expected (longer links have lower per-km cost). Significant.
Domestic links only (N=271). Positive, significant at 1%. Slightly larger magnitude than baseline.
International links only (N=142). Positive but insignificant at 5% (p=0.19). Smaller sample.
Drop links < 50km (N=409). Result unchanged. Significant at 1%.
Drop links > 800km (N=396). Result unchanged. Significant at 5%.
Drop top 5% trade costs (N=392). Coefficient smaller but significant at 1%.
Drop bottom 5% trade costs (N=392). Result stable. Significant at 1%.
Paved roads only (N=217). Negative coefficient, insignificant. Distance does not predict costs within paved roads.
Unpaved roads only (N=183). Much larger coefficient, significant at 1%. Distance matters more for unpaved roads.
Large market links only (popn>2, N=195). Positive, significant at 5%.
Links with at least one small market (N=218). Positive, significant at 5%.
Winsorized taubar at 1st/99th percentile. Result stable. Significant at 1%.
T6C5 specification without clustering. Distance still insignificant (p=0.57).
T6C5 with HC1 robust SE. Distance still insignificant (p=0.66).
Log-log specification for international links. Distance still insignificant (p=0.69).
Drop language from T6C5. Distance still insignificant.
Drop FTA from T6C5. Distance still insignificant.
Drop corruption from T6C5. Distance still insignificant.
Drop LPI from T6C5. Distance still insignificant.
Add population control to T6C5. Distance still insignificant.
Distance only for international links. Still insignificant (p=0.30).
Add GDP to T6C5. Distance coefficient essentially zero and insignificant.
Winsorized 5th/95th percentile for international links. Distance essentially zero.
Median regression for international links. Distance negative and insignificant.
Drop < 100km for international links (N=129). Distance near zero and insignificant.
Port regression without clustering. Corruption negative, marginally insignificant (p=0.11). Same coefficient.
Corruption + LPI only. Corruption negative but insignificant.
Drop GDP from A13C1. Corruption negative but insignificant.
Log outcome for port links. Corruption negative but insignificant.
OLS sigma estimation: lnsh ~ lnp, region-grain + country-year FE, cluster cgcode, N=463. sigma=1.49.

Country-year FE only (drop region-grain FE). Coefficient drops to 0.131, insignificant (p=0.66).
Region-grain FE only (drop country-year FE). Coefficient drops to 0.027, insignificant (p=0.74).
HC1 robust SE instead of clustering. Same coefficient, smaller SE, more significant (p=0.009).

No region FE. Larger coefficient (-0.40), highly significant. Suggests FE absorb some price variation.
